Description:
The Content Creator is responsible for the writing, design, and creation of digital content for assigned clients in various sectors (such as finance, entertainment, tech) accounts on various media platforms. In addition to taking an active part in content production activities, the person in the office will be asked to do translation and revision of texts in both English and French.
Compensation:
$50,000 - $70,000 yearly
Responsibilities:
Manage the production of content for clients, on a weekly basis, both in terms of quality control, and by taking care of meeting the deadlines required of its team;
Participate in the meetings to develop the digital content of the projects, and find working methods to stimulate creativity;
Create content and search for the visual material needed for various publications;
Integrating content and interactive elements on various media platforms;
Monitor existing content and implement web policies;
Assume the role of an expert in the agency's content and collaborate on client projects;
Create content with a high level of commitment to customers
Reread, develop and translate content in English and French
Qualifications:
Degree in communications, marketing, or another relevant discipline;
Bilingualism and impeccable command of both official languages (French and English, both written and spoken);
2 years of experience writing content, particularly in integration and publishing content on social media, an asset;
Strong ability to build good relationships with clients;
Creativity, adaptability, attention to detail, and team spirit;
In-depth knowledge and personal use of popular social media platforms (Facebook, LinkedIn, Instagram);
Strong knowledge of social media marketing trends;
Ability to lead multiple files simultaneously;
Strong interest in a career in marketing;
Increased knowledge of office software used (Suite MS Office).
About Company
Empower is an application that takes care of all the marketing needs of small and medium businesses through a fun interface encouraging marketing actions through automation and human experts.
We hire professionals who are eager to learn, grow, and help businesses in all industries succeed. We offer competitive salaries and benefits and our employees have the freedom to work anywhere in the world (or from any WeWork office) alongside a collaborative team, excellence, honesty, and fun!

Temporaire 1 an (congé de maternité)
